f{char} - foward until {char} is found
r - replace char where cursor is
o - will put you in insert mode under the current line ""USE INSTEAD OF <A> <ENTER>""
O - will put you in insert mode above the current line
C - change/delete remaining part of the line


# Visual mode

v - char visual mode
V - Line-wise visual mode
CTRL - v  Block-wise visual mode
gv - Reselect the last visual selection


